data.description: DON'T MISS THIS GEM!   Home is newly vacant and clean and ready for a new owner.  Gorgeous 4 bedroom 3.5 bath townhome/condo in amenity-rich Potomac Club.  Two car attached garage with rear entry.  Gourmet Kitchen with Stainless, Granite, table space and sliding door to the balcony.  Open Floor Plan.  Great room with Gas fireplace and separate dining area.  Upstairs with 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths.  Upstairs laundry.  Walk in to the Lower level with 4th bedroom and 3rd full bath. Close to shopping.  Gated Community.  Vacant.   Easy to Show.  Ready for quick closing!  Won't last long now!
